.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, reading, collecting, card-games, dancing
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, bike, skateboard, roller
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, snowboarding, swimming, rugby
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, satire, animation, zombie

1. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is hiking
2. the person driving the subway is the person watching scientific movies
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is reading
4. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is weightlifting
5. the person who's hobby is reading is to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting
6. the old-gold-smoker is the person watching zombie movies
7. the kools-smoker is the person who's hobby is card-games
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the person watching animation movies
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who's sport is swimming
13. the person driving the roller is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person driving the skateboard is to the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Transport	|   skateboard	|    bike	|     jet-ski	|    subway	|    roller	|
| Hobby		|    card-games	|      dancing	|      hiking	|     collecting	|     reading	|
| Sport	|     rugby	|      weightlifting	|      snowboarding	| swimming	|     skateboarding	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Movie-Genre		|     adventure	|     animation	|     zombie	|     scientific	|     satire	|
